":4,"text":"But the key here is her history of chronic tobacco chewing for 18 years.","dimension":11,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.084435,0.1261,0.11104,0.098163,0.094869,0.086402,0.081196,0.07578,0.0701,0.065203,0.057153,0.049555],"unified_progress":[0.071637,0.1007,0.10067,0.099178,0.094405,0.095846,0.088157,0.086872,0.077812,0.072375,0.061948,0.0504]},{"section":5,"text":"That's a long time, and I know that tobacco use, especially in chewing forms, can have various health implications.","dimension":17,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.05309,0.10737,0.11287,0.15014,0.09686,0.087435,0.082483,0.076532,0.069796,0.06361,0.054521,0.045281],"unified_progress":[0.041297,0.07702,0.095081,0.10516,0.10203,0.10027,0.099897,0.095792,0.089051,0.082687,0.066453,0.045259]},{"section":6,"text":"Her main symptom is difficulty opening her mouth, which is known as trismus.","dimension":14,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.058443,0.1022,0.10131,0.099352,0.095559,0.089759,0.087076,0.082845,0.077521,0.071811,0.069249,0.064878],"unified_progress":[0.058556,0.089381,0.0928,0.096139,0.096796,0.095385,0.092676,0.091395,0.085686,0.078684,0.067669,0.054834]},{"section":7,"text":"Trismus is a condition where the mouth can't be fully opened, and it can be caused by several factors.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.048487,0.078106,0.090605,0.099757,0.099032,0.097337,0.098008,0.093817,0.088076,0.079212,0.069225,0.058338],"unified_progress":[0.044408,0.074363,0.091087,0.099824,0.1031,0.10277,0.099579,0.094977,0.093195,0.080814,0.066163,0.049717]},{"section":8,"text":"I'm thinking about what could cause this in someone with a history of tobacco chewing.","dimension":17,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.051622,0.082337,0.088839,0.09526,0.09287,0.092288,0.091479,0.090394,0.086806,0.087098,0.07548,0.065526],"unified_progress":[0.044955,0.07401,0.084312,0.093231,0.09529,0.095903,0.097349,0.096225,0.091775,0.090521,0.076595,0.059834]},{"section":9,"text":"One possibility that comes to mind is\u53e3\u8154\u767d\u6591\u75c5 (leukoplakia), but that's more about white patches in the mouth and might not directly cause trismus.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.035977,0.067245,0.081911,0.092672,0.096453,0.097871,0.10166,0.099953,0.094854,0.088647,0.077317,0.065445],"unified_progress":[0.033129,0.063928,0.08386,0.0952,0.10036,0.10408,0.10285,0.099946,0.096746,0.089737,0.073897,0.056265]},{"section":10,"text":"Another thought is\u53e3\u8154\u764c (oral cancer), which can lead to stiffness or difficulty opening the mouth if it affects the muscles or jaw.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.041443,0.060686,0.074145,0.083628,0.092931,0.097586,0.10283,0.10319,0.1004,0.092736,0.082023,0.068395],"unified_progress":[0.04072,0.066839,0.082142,0.092983,0.098686,0.10242,0.10087,0.09888,0.096268,0.088615,0.074233,0.057346]},{"section":11,"text":"But she's been chewing tobacco for a long time, which is a known risk factor for oral cancer.","dimension":3,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.043444,0.073182,0.077522,0.082775,0.088572,0.092355,0.096947,0.098835,0.098795,0.09369,0.084031,0.069852],"unified_progress":[0.045386,0.071805,0.082225,0.088562,0.093584,0.10087,0.098637,0.0991,0.094165,0.090312,0.076333,0.059017]},{"section":12,"text":"Wait, but there's another condition called \u53e3\u8154\u7ea4\u7ef4\u5316 (oral fibromucositis) or more specifically, \u7600\u8840\u6027\u53e3\u708e (lichen sclerosus), but I'm not sure.","dimension":15,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.029379,0.056332,0.071649,0.08125,0.094133,0.099638,0.10736,0.10818,0.10316,0.096401,0.082915,0.069597],"unified_progress":[0.03128,0.061187,0.084446,0.095094,0.1008,0.10751,0.10532,0.10138,0.097505,0.089494,0.071841,0.054147]},{"section":13,"text":"Alternatively, there's a condition called \u53e3\u8154\u7c98\u8